\begin_layout Standard
If Victor exited the highway at this point (using a road that does not appear
 on the map) and drove 3 kilometers southeast, the second leg of Victor's
 journey could be captured by the vector 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[\begin{array}{c}
